file.name: contract-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Contract Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.1

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultipleContract:
      type: object
      required:
        - total
        - contracts
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        contracts:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Contract'
    Contract:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        provider_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        quantity:
          type: integer
        unit:
          type: string
        license_type:
          type: string
          enum: [ Corporation, User ]
        contract_type:
          type: string
          enum: [ outright, prepaid, automatic_updating_flat_rate, automatic_updating_measured_rate ]
        span_type:
          type: string
          enum: [ daily, weekly, monthly, yearly ]
        span_number:
          type: integer
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [ active, inactive, owner_absent, suspend ]
        purchased_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        issued_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        expires_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        status_change_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractItem'
        owner:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractOwner'
    ContractItem:
      type: object
      properties:
        item_id:
          type: string
        plan_id:
          type: string
    ContractOwner:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        name:
          type: string
        phone_number:
          type: string
        phone_number_2:
          type: string
        address:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractOwnerAddress'
    ContractOwnerAddress:
      type: object
      properties:
        country:
          type: string
          description: ISO 3166-1 alpha-2
        zip_code:
          type: string
        state:
          type: string
        city:
          type: string
        address_1:
          type: string
        address_2:
          type: string
        tags:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        custom_fields:
          type: object
    MultipleContractUser:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        users:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractUser'
    ContractUser:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        type:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        family_name:
          type: string
        given_name:
          type: string
        phonetic_family_name:
          type: string
        phonetic_given_name:
          type: string
        phone_number:
          type: string
        phone_number_2:
          type: string
        language:
          type: string
          enum: [ ja, en, en-US, de-DE, fr-FR, es-ES ]
          description: ISO639
        picture:
          type: string
          description: uri
        email:
          type: string
        emails:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        role:
          type: string
          enum: [ super_admin, staff ]
        category:
          type: string
          enum: [ member, guest ]
        address:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractOwnerAddress'
        license:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContractUserLicense'
    ContractUserLicense:
      type: object
      properties:
        issued_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        expires_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
